      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7ca80a94e9198587b6aa67"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "We've left the moon's orbit and reached the planet without interference from any more of those unidentified attackers. \n\nThe <i>[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAdamastor],Adamastor]]</i>'s survivors already left with their part of the treasure, and I recommend we leave this system immediately, in case someone recognizes us.",
