    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd8d47fff823c129399bad1"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Pilot Meyer, please do so. \n\nWe have a meeting with Lord Alexander in [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreDumassas],Dumassas]] that we're going to attend to next. ",
