      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cf884c01cbb0d5efcc2ad5d"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Captain Kamea, the commander has a point.\n\nYou said the <i>Adamastor</i> was supposed to be a part of the [[DM.Factions[faction_InterstellarExpeditions],Interstellar Expeditions]] operation but now it's blown to bits on the moon's surface.",
      "branches": [
