      "text": "Also, we hardly recovered any salvage with the exception of the Captain's new [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRoyal],Royal]] <i>Kintaro</i>. \n\nIt is one helluva machine but we could have gotten so much more from that cache.",
