      "text": "Yeah, Yang sounded rather enthusiastic during the mission and I think it was not just the 'Mechs he saw down there.\n\nWhich reminds me: it's the third time we've encountered unidentified 'Mechs with advanced technology in this region and now they're using space ships to perform attacks. ",
